quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,"By the forceful chargers"
  79,2,"raring to go,"
  79,3,"sweeping ahead at full stretch,"
  79,4,"overtaking swiftly"
  79,5,"to bring the matter to an end,"
  79,6,"on the Day when the blast reverberates"
  79,7,"and the second blast follows,"
  79,8,"hearts will tremble"
  79,9,"and eyes will be downcast."
  79,10,"They say, ‘What? shall we be brought back to life,"